manifest.name: Markdown Table Editor
manifest.description: An Obsidian plugin to provide an editor for Markdown tables. It can open CSV, Microsoft Excel/Google Sheets data as Markdown tables from Obsidian Markdown editor.
manifest.author: Ganessh Kumar R P <rpganesshkumar@gmail.com>
